Text on Image - The Things We Do, Do Things to Us
image:image.image:caption: We do not live in a time or culture that is conducive to the spiritual health and vitality we see offered to us in Scripture. The Bible shows us examples of an abundant, joyful, others-centered and Godward life that often feel far from reality. Apathy, distraction, self-reliance, cynicism and self-absorption steal our joy and rot us from the inside out. Join us as we take 5 months to fight these things with everything we have--to fight for our joy, peace, vitality, and flourishing as humans made to image and be filled by the God.
